                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                     <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                        <locus target="#109va">109va-</locus>vb: ተ{ፈ}ጸመ፡ መዝገበ፡ ቅዳሴ፡ በ፲ወ፱፻፵ወ፭ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት፡
                        ዘመነ፡ መንግሥቱ፡ ለንጉሥነ፡ ኃይለ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ጳጳስ፡ አቡነ፡ ይስሐቅ፡ በወርኃ፡ መስከረም፡ ፲ወ፭መዓልት፡ ዓበቅቴ፡ ፲፭እንዘ፡
                        ሀሎ።<locus target="#109va">109va-</locus>vb: The collection of Liturgies was
                        completed in the Year of Mercy 1945, the reign of our King Ḫāyla Śǝllāse,
                        (under) bishop ʾabuna Yǝsḥaq, in the month of Maskaram, on the 15th day, during
                        the 15th epact. The Ms. is dated to Thursday, 15 Maskaram 1945 year of mercy (=
                        25 September 1952 A.D.) </colophon>
                  </msItem>
                  
